#: ../../content/guides/quirks/quirk-disable_devmode_ignore_cache.md:2
msgid "Quirk `releng.disable_devmode_ignore_cache`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/quirks/quirk-disable_devmode_ignore_cache.md:7
msgid ""
"Packages may be configured with [`LIBFOO_DEVMODE_IGNORE_CACHE`](pkg-opt-"
"devmode-ignore-cache) to always attempt a new fetch of sources for a "
"development-configured revision. However, if a remote is not available "
"during a rebuild event, the process will fail since the package cannot be "
"re-fetched from the configured site. To help a builder hint that using the "
"cache is fine for an invoke, this quirk can be provided to avoid any re-"
"fetch attempt."
msgstr ""

